# PIT Module

The Personal Income Tax module estimates tax liability at taxpayer level or household level.

## Main policy parameters

The PIT module can include:

- tax rates;
- tax brackets;
- personal allowances;
- deductions;
- exemptions;
- special regimes;
- withholding tax rates.

